  BuffName: Elemental Resonance
  Description: 'The ElementalDeer synchronize the rotating Elemental Pillars (Fire,
    Frost, Lightning, Wind) to break its defenses. Each match increases damage taken
    by 5% and grants a buff (Fire: damage, Frost: regenerates HP, Lightning: increases
    SP cost, Wind: evasion). Matching all four elements purges its buffs and Stuns
    it for 3 turns; upon recovery, it temporarily gains all buffs.'
